<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:20:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>首席执行官表示星展银行将把中国证券合资公司的股权提高到91%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/dbs-moving-raise-china-securities-joint-venture-stake-91-ceo-says-2024-09-25/</link><description>星展集团首席执行官皮尤什·古普塔 (Piyush Gupta) 周三表示，该集团正在将其在中国证券合资企业的所有权从 51% 增加到 91%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/dbs-moving-raise-china-securities-joint-venture-stake-91-ceo-says-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国新刺激计划引起全球市场轰动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-new-stimulus-plans-make-splash-global-markets-2024-09-25/</link><description>在北京宣布自疫情大流行以来最大规模的刺激措施后，中国敞口资产周二大幅上涨，以期使世界第二大经济体摆脱今年震动全球货币和股市的通缩恐慌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-new-stimulus-plans-make-splash-global-markets-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国的货币政策忽视了对经济增长的关键威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-monetary-volleys-miss-key-threat-economic-growth-2024-09-25/</link><description>中国央行已转向更为激进的宽松立场，但其政策武器并未将经济增长的主要敌人：持续疲软的消费者需求纳入考虑范围。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:56:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-monetary-volleys-miss-key-threat-economic-growth-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>印尼称赞中国公司为陷入困境的新资本的首个外国投资者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-hails-chinese-firm-first-foreign-investor-troubled-new-capital-2024-09-25/</link><description>周三，印度尼西亚总统佐科·维多多(Joko Widodo)在这个东南亚国家陷入困境的婆罗洲岛新首都为一家中国公司的房地产综合体破土动工，并称赞这是一项具有吸引力的外国投资先驱。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:43:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-hails-chinese-firm-first-foreign-investor-troubled-new-capital-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>泰国汽车业因订单下降和家庭债务飙升而举步维艰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/thai-auto-sector-reels-falling-orders-soaring-household-debt-2024-09-25/</link><description>泰国价值 530 亿美元的汽车工业正面临严峻的未来，因为负债累累的国内消费者难以筹集购买资金，而其主要传统汽车的海外买家越来越多地转向电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:16:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/thai-auto-sector-reels-falling-orders-soaring-household-debt-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>大众劳资冲突凸显欧洲汽车工厂难题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-labour-clash-spotlights-europes-car-factory-conundrum-2024-09-25/</link><description>路透社对欧洲六家汽车制造商的工厂产能利用率数据进行的审查显示，大众汽车并不是一个例外。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-labour-clash-spotlights-europes-car-factory-conundrum-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国刺激制糖热潮之后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-25/</link><description>凯文·巴克兰 (Kevin Buckland) 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 04:34:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚财长本周将访问中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-treasurer-travel-china-this-week-2024-09-25/</link><description>澳大利亚财长吉姆·查尔默斯表示，他将于本周前往中国与中国同行举行会谈，这是澳大利亚财长七年来首次进行此类访问。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 03:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-treasurer-travel-china-this-week-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲其他地区举步维艰，中国股市延续刺激性涨势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-25/</link><description>中国股市周三大幅上涨，将刺激措施推动的涨势延续到第二天，尽管该地区其他股市表现不佳，原油从数周高位回落。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:51:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国解放军罕见公开试射洲际弹道导弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-pla-launches-intercontinental-ballistic-missile-into-pacific-ocean-2024-09-25/</link><description>中国周三表示，它罕见地向太平洋发射了一枚洲际弹道导弹，此举可能会引发国际社会对中国核建设的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:17:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-pla-launches-intercontinental-ballistic-missile-into-pacific-ocean-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>“渔网”：警察配额、监视将朝鲜人困在中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fishing-net-police-quotas-surveillance-trap-north-koreans-china-2024-09-25/</link><description>中国在与朝鲜的 1,400 公里边境上建立了新的驱逐中心、数百个智能面部识别摄像头和额外的船只巡逻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fishing-net-police-quotas-surveillance-trap-north-koreans-china-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行下调中期贷款利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-cuts-medium-term-loan-rate-2024-09-25/</link><description>中国央行周三降低了银行中期贷款成本，此举与前一天宣布的旨在提振经济的广泛政策宽松措施一致。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:57:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-cuts-medium-term-loan-rate-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>担心中国刺激计划不足以提振需求，油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-steady-china-stimulus-hopes-fade-us-crude-stockpiles-fall-2024-09-25/</link><description>油价周三下跌，因投资者重新评估中国经济刺激计划是否足以推动全球最大原油进口国的燃料需求增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:50:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-steady-china-stimulus-hopes-fade-us-crude-stockpiles-fall-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚、新西兰元因中国经济刺激措施而大放异彩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/australian-new-zealand-dollars-scale-new-highs-china-boost-2024-09-25/</link><description>周三，澳元和新西兰元触及数月高位，而人民币则触及一年多以来的最高水平，因中国激进的经济刺激计划为风险偏好注入了最新一剂强心剂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:47:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/australian-new-zealand-dollars-scale-new-highs-china-boost-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园服务以4.46亿美元出售珠海万达股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/country-garden-services-sell-stake-zhuhai-wanda-446-mln-2024-09-25/</link><description>此次出售使该公司能够简化投资、回收资本并重新专注于核心业务。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:14:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/country-garden-services-sell-stake-zhuhai-wanda-446-mln-2024-09-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>